{"tid":2355164,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"新垣結衣  Switch 無字廣告獲激讚","createTime":"2021-01-06T03:15:36.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-06T11:52:25.000Z","uid":25345,"like":24,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"85cc1b032259561cd2b2ac5dee9d64d9e9d142b3","tid":2355164,"uid":25345,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:15:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210104/422863811188363264375648.jpeg/QoOnx8t4FEEVKzT9Z6Ll_cwyRVLV1Zcdsb2Je7G9iXs?v=w1280r16_9\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210104%2F422863811188363264375648.jpeg%2FQoOnx8t4FEEVKzT9Z6Ll_cwyRVLV1Zcdsb2Je7G9iXs%3Fv%3Dw1280r16_9&h=bd68334b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n去年日本最受歡迎女星你未必能說出名字，但提到華人圈人氣最高的日本女星，就定是被封「國民老婆」的新垣結衣！知名遊戲商任天堂為旗下主機Nintendo Switch推出新一波廣告，只見代言人新垣結衣瞓在被窩拿着Switch在玩，廣告上除了任天堂和Switch商標以外，隻字全無。正所謂一切盡在不言中，任天堂這個無字廣告，引來網民大讚該公司深明廣告之道！<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/dw/20210104/422794145040437248498751.jpeg/8Ne4GsxDdreW6s7OIgiW1jFl-pzsaRSyOhrxnToa8Z0?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2Fdw%2F20210104%2F422794145040437248498751.jpeg%2F8Ne4GsxDdreW6s7OIgiW1jFl-pzsaRSyOhrxnToa8Z0%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=683736c5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n知名遊戲商任天堂為旗下主機Nintendo Switch推出新一輯冬季廣告，平面版本已於早前公開。近年Switch代言人一直都是不論日本國內外都人氣高企的新垣結衣，廣告亦備受網民好評。然而有網民發現，最新的Nintendo Switch廣告，不設文任文案，直接是結衣拿着Switch在被窩玩的照片。<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://images2.gamme.com.tw/news2/2020/22/38/pJyRpp6YmKWbsKQ.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimages2.gamme.com.tw%2Fnews2%2F2020%2F22%2F38%2FpJyRpp6YmKWbsKQ.jpg&h=b76183cb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n網民幾乎一面倒地大讚廣告出色，有人形容「完美表現出Switch的攜帶性還帶有季節感」，亦有人認為這樣才是真正好廣告的本質，表示「這種沒有多餘的文字的廣告才更能表達出商品的魅力」、「真正有魅力的商品根本不用寫一堆『熱賣』、『好評』之類的東西」。<br />\n<br />\n「在日本是很少見類型的廣告。這種的也很不錯」<br />\n日本で珍しいタイプの広告だ<br />\nこういうのがいいんだよ<br />\n<br />\n「第一眼看到就能傳達『Switch超棒的！』。以廣告來說也很棒，想出的人真是天才！」<br />\nパッと見ただけで「Switch最高！」ってのが伝わる<br />\n広告としても最高、思いつきそうで出てこない、考えた人は天才！<br />\n<br />\n「有新垣結衣就只會覺得文字其他的東西出現很礙眼了」<br />\n新垣結衣がいる時点で文字等は邪魔にしかならないのかもしれん<br />\n<br />\n「看來是新垣結衣的大勝利...」<br />\nガッキー大勝利のようです&hellip;"},{"pid":"de818b557df41544c239b4e17f6ec997966dd5f7","tid":2355164,"uid":139224,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:18:57.000Z","msg":"結衣<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"48ccbf683566a24784e64b256b5b2f706a057e75","tid":2355164,"uid":93096,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:36:25.000Z","msg":"勁靚...<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"30bfb1363d5df4bbb42c0612fc69ae1065eb69de","tid":2355164,"uid":51121,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:40:45.000Z","msg":"明星既作用."},{"pid":"63802fb2d6f02fecd204ef05bb668cae0c38fc18","tid":2355164,"uid":53463,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:45:39.000Z","msg":"吹水啦 , 寫到成版都係字只要唔遮住結衣個樣都話好睇㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/06.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d4af8ba9eea6f44c50faf55323dfe19eed707ce","tid":2355164,"uid":32442,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:48:49.000Z","msg":"Viu播得好密 但次次都睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6c7b99529a59bc22a6070b79ae9a0643f4d4821e","tid":2355164,"uid":330227,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"quote":{"pid":"9d4af8ba9eea6f44c50faf55323dfe19eed707ce","tid":2355164,"uid":32442,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T03:48:49.000Z","msg":"Viu播得好密 但次次都睇哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-06T04:52:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br 